name: MPL Official
description:
**Check if your bootcamp player is claimed by searching for the character ID (e.g. #4201) in our [bootcamp player collection](https://opensea.io/collection/mpl-bootcamp)**

The Martian Premier League is a collection of 10,000 unique human and Martian characters living on the Ethereum blockchain. These characters are your route into the Martian Premier League game: a ‘football manager’ style game where holders can train, trade and compete in the MPL league. Over time there will be further application for these genesis characters outside of the first MPL game. Visit www.martianpremierleague.com for more details and t&cs.

name: EightBit Me
description:
[EightBit](https://www.eightbit.me) is a collection of 8,888 NFT’s that are generated by countless 8-bit themed traits. Within the collection, there are rare outfits, items, and more surprises.

Each NFT contains a PFP and a full Digital EightBit Character which are stored on IPFS. All characters have their own page ([see example](https://www.eightbit.me/bit/7030)) that will become more interactive in time.

Back in 2010, we launched the original 8-bit avatar creator. Before a world of punks and apes, our app let you make a virtual 8-bit version of yourself. Check out it out in action [here](https://vimeo.com/20713468).

name: [ Ledger ] Market Pass - Genesis Edition
description:
[ Ledger ] Market is the most secure platform for artists and brands to release their NFTs, where Ledger customers can securely connect through Ledger Live and clear sign their transactions. For first access to exclusive collaborations, and Ledger hardware, software and services, become a [ Ledger ] Market Pass holder.


[ L ] Market’s brand mark is a generative font with over two billion unique variations. It speaks to: 1) the massive awareness generative art and PFP projects have brought to blockchain technology, and 2) the advanced cryptography built into Ledger and [ Ledger ] Market’s DNA.

name: Lacoste UNDW3: Genesis Pass
description:
Lacoste UNDW3: Genesis Pass is a 11,212 collection on the Ethereum Blockchain, acting as Round 1 of the UNDW3 experience.

Pioneers taking part in this adventure will follow the Lacoste brand on a collaborative journey having access to all the upcoming perks and privileges.

name: "MOAR" by Joan Cornella
description: ** MOAR by Joan Cornellà ** is an unusual mansion in the metaverse proudly presented by FWENCLUB, where 5,555 creatures with their souls minted with the ERC721 blockchain as NFTs. Each of these "peacefully-living-together" humans, cyborgs or even zombies, is unique, hand-drawn by Spanish artist Joan Cornellà using over 200 unique attributes. You may even find shops, games, virtual exhibitions … and MOAR!

name: VeeCon  Tickets
description: VeeCon 2022 is a multi-day superconference where only VeeCon NFT ticket holders will experience an extraordinary lineup of content including iconic keynote speeches; innovative and educational talks, panels and Q&A sessions; and many collaborative experiences

name: Milady Maker
description: Milady Maker is a collection of 10,000 generative pfpNFT's in a neochibi aesthetic inspired by street style tribes.

name: VeeFriends
description: A Gary Vaynerchuk NFT project around meaningful intellectual property and an extraordinary community.

name: World of Women
description:
A community celebrating representation, inclusivity, and equal opportunities for all.
United by a first-of-its-kind collection, featuring 10,000 artworks of diverse and powerful women.

Created and Illustrated by Yam Karkai (@ykarkai)

New official collection World of Women Galaxy available here:
https://opensea.io/collection/world-of-women-galaxy

name: uwucrew
description:
uwucrew is a woman co-founded generative collection of 9670 avatars inspired by anime and pop culture, aiming to be both inclusive and expressive. Every uwucrew NFT is completely unique and features up to 9 traits with 140+ assets. 

uwucrew features an incredibly vibrant art-focused community with a focus on artist support and representation.

Made with love by uwulabs
